message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with audio signal processing and analysis. Other likely categories could be cs.CV (computer vision) as the proposed method is inspired by Faster-RCNN, a well-known visual object detection framework, cs.LG (machine learning) as the proposed method uses a convolutional recurrent neural network, cs.CL (computation and language) as the method deals with audio event detection, which is related to speech and language processing, and cs.MM (multimedia) as the method deals with audio data and multimedia analysis.
